room_title: Escape room "The Bunker" by Escape Oakland in San Francisco
room_description: A famous and brilliant scientist turned recluse was found dead by hikers in a remote location somewhere in Northern California. You are a team of local park rangers called to come check out the site. While searching near the location of his demise you found a hidden bunker. Door ajar, lights on, it must’ve belonged to the scientist. It's time to go in and check out what he’s been up to in there!
